  "about": "Year: First Year\nBirthday: November 13th\nBlood type: B\nHeight: 149 cm\nBWH: 71-52-75\n\nRina is not great at conveying emotions through her face. Because of this, she makes use of her \"Rina-Chan Board\", which is a sketchbook she uses to draw her emotions onto.\n\nRina shows a strong interest in science. She excels in science and maths but struggles with her Japanese class. Rina is great at arcades and video games, and also shows a fondness for animals.",
